            <title>[PIG-3316] Pig failed to interpret DateTime values in some special cases</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3316</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For the query&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A = load &apos;date.txt&apos; as ( f1:int, f2:datetime );&lt;br/&gt;
dump A;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;with input data&lt;br/&gt;
1,1970-01-01&lt;br/&gt;
2,1970-01&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;pig generates the following output&lt;br/&gt;
(1,1970-01-01T00:00:00.000-01:00)&lt;br/&gt;
(2,1970-01-01T00:00:00.000-01:00)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;which seemingly incorrectly interprets the day or month part as time zone.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
